{"about_the_game":"War Selection is a pseudo-historical real-time strategy with base building, resource extraction and warfare.<br><br>Players battle for supremacy against dozens of opponents on a unique procedurally generated map.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Every Player Starts In the stone Age. </h2>During the course of the match, the player is at first able to select a particular culture, and then a specific country. <br>This allows to showcase the entire historical diversity of human civilization within the game.<br><br>Each evolutionary path brings its own unique game experience. <br><br>Depending on that path, game mechanics and other possibilities are expanded.<br><br>Having passed through 7 historical eras, the player reaches the age of heavy tanks and long-range artillery.<br><br>The game features more than 100 buildings and more than 200 distinct land, air and naval units.<br><br>War Selection features several unique game modes:<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Survival \u2014 A mode where you need to survive against hordes of enemies;<br></li><li>Free for all;<br></li><li>Ranked 1 vs 1 and 2 vs 2;<br></li><li>Tug of War;<br></li><li>Team match;<br></li><li>Armageddon \u2014 A Battle Royale flavored mode where players with the least amount of territory are bombarded by meteors until only one player remains.</li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1022450/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1735806660","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1022450/page.bg.jpg?t=1735806660","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1022450/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1735806660","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1022450/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1735806660","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Online PvP","id":36},{"descript